'''希臘語族'''是[[印歐語系|印歐語系]]下屬語族之一<ref>In other contexts, "Hellenic" and "Greek" are generally synonyms.</ref>。一般來說，希臘語族只包括[[希臘語|希臘語]]一種語言 <ref name="Browning">Browning (1983), ''Medieval and Modern Greek'', Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</ref><ref name="JosephPhilippaki">Joseph, Brian D. and Irene Philippaki-Warburton (1987): ''Modern Greek''. London: Routledge, p. 1.</ref>。但一些語言學家認為希臘語可以拆分為多種語言<ref name="BJoseph">B. Joseph (2001): "Ancient Greek". In: J. Garry et al. (eds.) ''Facts about the World's Major Languages: An Encyclopedia of the World's Major Languages, Past and Present.'' ([http://www.ling.ohio-state.edu/~bjoseph/articles/gancient.htm Online Paper] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ling.ohio-state.edu/~bjoseph/articles/gancient.htm |date=20161001113024 }})</ref>。

